listings.comment: Fawad is an exceptional talent when it comes to web design and everything related to websites. Our organization had an existing website built with Elementor on WordPress, and we needed revisions to both the content and design. Not only was Fawad patient throughout the process, but he also communicated effectively, ensuring that every issue we had was resolved. My team is beyond satisfied with his work, and we’ll absolutely be using him for future projects. I highly recommend and fully endorse the quality of his work. If you’re looking for a web designer who pays attention to detail and goes above and beyond to ensure you love the final product, look no further than Fawad. Honestly, if a 10-star rating existed, he’d have mine!

The website they created for me has malware.  It’s costing me hundreds of dollars to get this fixed and I’m losing so much money because my clients cannot access my website because of this issue. I attempted to give them the opportunity to remove the malware, but they did not seem very knowledgeable. Still insisting the website is safe, although I can’t even access it from my own computer because of my virus protection. In addition to several different companies, rejecting my emails because of the website issues.

I’m happy that i choosed Fawad to helping me creating my website, he went above and beyond to reach my expectations and he’s very professional and absolute expert in what he do. Thank you so much Fawad for your great effort and I will continue to use your services again in the future!

Fawad Ahmed developed a website that was exactly what we were looking for. His attention to detail and professionalism were second to none. He delivered within the timeframe he promised. I will definitely use Fawad's services for future projects. I will also recommend Fawad to others.

He is very skilled and he exceeded my expectations.
He delivered on time and with a very high quality.
I highly recommend his services and i will buy again from him.
